headline: GCM Grosvenor Inc. (GCMG) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: GCM Grosvenor (GCMG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +11.76% and +2.38%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Franklin Resources, Inc. Announces Preliminary Month-End Assets Under Management
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., November 05, 2025--Franklin Resources, Inc. (Franklin Templeton) (NYSE: BEN) today reported preliminary month-end assets under management (AUM) of $1.69 trillion at October 31, 2025, compared to $1.66 trillion at September 30, 2025.
